story: Hisham Abd El-Hafez Eid shared NASA Space Apps Cairo's photo to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: NASA Space Apps Cairo
description:
The Space Apps Challenge Hackathon wouldn't be complete without passionate mentors sharing their insights on how to find solutions in the 4 categories; Robotics, Outer Space, Humans and Earth.

If you have the spirit, time and energy for a 48-hour hackathon, and ready to share your valuable expertise in solving the Space Apps Challenges, you're more than welcome to join us!

Join us now here > http://spaceappscairo.com/mentors.html

Read more on the challenges > http://goo.gl/hGyA8F
